---
title: Bacon and Lentil Shepherd's Pie with Mushrooms and Cheese
description: Versatile and aromatic, this roasted spice & herb blend gives any dish a tasty boost. Made with many fragrant herbs and spices, this spice blend contains ingredients such as paprika, chipotle chilli, ground coriander and thyme, making it perfect for flavouring chicken and meat koftas, as well as a flavour driver in veggie traybakes and stews.
